                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.6363 Standard Oil/318½: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Teheran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gotlieb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-12-20T18:00:00+03:25">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 20, 1923—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received December 20—4:28 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>This afternoon I officially witnessed signing of north Persian oil concession by
                    Reza Khan, Prime Minister, and R. Soper representing Sinclair Exploration
                    Company. I shall send text as soon as possible.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gotlieb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
